User nikdoof
AddKeysToAgent yes
CanonicalizeHostname yes
CanonicalDomains int.doofnet.uk doofnet.uk lab.doofnet.uk

Include ~/.orbstack/ssh/config
Include config-*

Host *
    ForwardX11 no
    ForwardX11Trusted no
    Protocol 2
    TCPKeepAlive yes
    ServerAliveInterval 60
    ServerAliveCountMax 30
    VerifyHostKeyDNS ask
